data.description: Introducing A Charming 4-Bedroom, 3 full Bath Home with Unique Character.  Step away from the cookie-cutter designs and discover something different that exudes charm and individuality. This home, nestled in Lantern Ridge, is truly a cutie that stands out from the rest.  As you walk up you are greeted with a beautiful front porch, offering plenty of space to share with friends and family and enjoy the outdoors.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the beautiful wood-look tile that graces the flooring, adding a touch of warmth and sophistication. The spacious living room is designed for grand gatherings and cozy evenings, offering ample room for relaxation and entertaining. The updated kitchen is a dream come true for any culinary enthusiast, with modern fixtures and a brand-new refrigerator replaced in 2023. A large dining area is perfect for hosting family dinners or intimate gatherings, allowing you to create cherished memories. "	This home boasts four generously sized bedrooms, each offering ample space for comfort and personalization. The master bathroom has been thoughtfully updated, providing a retreat-like ambiance to unwind and rejuvenate. Upstairs, you'll find two large bedrooms and a full bathroom, offering a versatile space that can be utilized as a separate living area for teens, guests, or even in-laws, providing privacy and independence. For those who love the outdoors, this property offers extra parking space, ideal for your boat, RV, or any other recreational vehicles you treasure. The fully fenced backyard is a private oasis where you can relax and entertain. It even features a cozy fire pit, making it the perfect spot to gather with friends and family, creating cherished moments under the open sky. Roof is 2021. HVAC 2016. Fridge 2023. Don't miss your chance to make this distinctive property your new home...
